property.short_description:
Everything you love about the river in one house! Plenty of room to spread out and relax. The ultimate view from the upstairs balcony and river access downstairs. with a private dock, pool table, 2 kitchens &amp; 5 bedrooms this house has it all! Fully stocked with everything you need for the perfect river getaway!&nbsp;<br />
<br />
&nbsp;

Parker Strip pool house with game room!&nbsp;Beautiful mountain views from the patio and the pool! If you ever decide to leave the amazing backyard there is plenty to do inside.<br />
